<plot>Becky's Story is a look at the results of Abstinence-Only Sex Education from the point of view of one teen mother. Becky tells her story in her own words - from taking the virginity pledge at church to juggling motherhood, work and school. Becky explained that she didn't think she would get pregnant because she usually timed things around her period. Now she advocates comprehensive sex education and confidential access to birth control for teens who are sexually active.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?062830</url></doc>
